<item>
 <title>Group Assurance Policy</title>
 <link>https://www.wapic.com/node/160</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Product Brief:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Group Life assurance scheme is an insurance solution designed for staffs of corporate organizations and members of associations and social clubs. It provides financial protection for loved ones of an employee working in organization or member of an association in case of demise whilst in service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Target Market:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Corporations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Benefits&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The benefits payable under the policy is tax free&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefits upon demise is paid to the beneficiaries of the deceased employee&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discharges any responsibilities employers may feel towards staff’s dependants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It aids employers in attracting and retain best quality staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mitigates employer’s unplanned financial payout associated with the death of an employee&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fosters good relationship between the employer and the employees as the employee is rest assured that his/her loved one would not be financially strained&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;gt;It relieves associations and friends from the burden of contributing toward the financial needs of a bereaved member’s family&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It relieves the government of the burden of providing for employees’ family and liberates the society of the menace of social problems of disintegrate family members arising from death of a bread-winner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;•	It gives a creditor sufficient level of comfort to advance loan which indirectly contributes toward the growth of an economy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Features&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;It is an yearly renewable policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Death Benefit is a minimum of three times the annual emolument for employee coverage according the Pension reform Act of 2014&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It provides optional cover for critical illness, burial expense, terminal/ accelerated benefit, accidental medical benefit, permanent disability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It also accommodates spousal benefits for employees on a scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Premium payment is annual&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guaranteed death benefit becomes payable upon demise within the specified period&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sum assured can be increased by the policyholder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;There must be a minimum of three (3) persons to incept cover&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It covers death as a result of any occurrence except suicide&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It provides worldwide coverage &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Retirement age is determined per scheme but to a maximum of 65 yrs. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical Examination may be required for some members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Policy Documentation&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Completed proposal form&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Copy of vehicle license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proof of ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h4&gt;How it Works&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Proposer provides Wapic with the names, dates of birth, annual emolument/sum assured of each member with the selected options (if any)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wapic computes the provisional premium payable &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proposer accepts premium payable, fills required Proposal Form &amp;amp; provides KYC documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proposer makes premium payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wapic issues policy document and advises members to undergo medical examination (where necessary)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wapic issues policy document&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-insurance-category field-type-list-text field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Insurance Category:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;GROUP&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-corporate-image field-type-image field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Corporate Image:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://www.wapic.com/sites/default/files/GroupLife.jpg&quot; width=&quot;350&quot; height=&quot;253&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-product-summary field-type-text field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Product Summary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Group Life assurance scheme is an insurance solution designed for staffs of corporate organizations ...&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
